data.description: Lovely 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath home in beautiful Barton Woods subdivision. Home sits in a park-like setting on a cul-de-sac that is connected to trails to the park, fishing ponds, playgrounds and picnic areas. This great family home is Energy Efficient with Radiant Attic Barrier, Insulated Low/E windows and High-Efficiency HVAC>13 SEER. Lots of house for the family to enjoy, featuring large game room, media room and family room with fireplace. The backyard is huge with plenty of room for a pool.
